txt.en: Corsairs and Gondorian freebooters can be found at Azruthor's Rue and throughout Tarlang's Crown.\n\nWhile exploring the ruined remains of Azruthor's encampment in Tarlang's Crown, you have encountered a number of Gondorian freebooters and Corsairs of Umbar. You should defeat them and make safe the road through Tarlang's Crown.
